REACTION    malonyl-CoA + an anthocyanidin 3-O-beta-D-glucoside = CoA + an anthocyanidin 3-O-(6-O-malonyl-beta-D-glucoside) [RN:R07255]
ALL_REAC    R07255 > R06801 R06817 R07938
